commit.message: Hide obvious suggestion from cli output

 LL | use std::fmt::{self, self};
-   |                ------^^^^
-   |                |   | |

+   |                ----  ^^^^ `fmt` reimported here
+   |                |
    |                previous import of the module `fmt` here
    |
    = note: `fmt` must be defined only once in the type namespace of this module
